(190, 1, '2015-03-04 07:07:14', '2015-03-04 07:07:14', '[vc_row][vc_column width="1/1"][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/2"][vc_single_image image="132" img_size="full" image_position="normal-align-left" has_link="false" link_type="normal"][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/2"][uxb_heading text="HOW I CAPTURE YOUR WEDDING DAY" type="h2" has_line="false" icon_size="16"][vc_column_text]Your Wedding photo shoot gives you the snap-shot to your wedding day, the glamour of dressing up and yet very relaxing and fun. We capture some special moments around the magical city of Sydney.\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Enhance the experience of your day</li>\r\n	<li>End product in mind  wedding album and wall art with quality to last through family generations</li>\r\n	<li>Make you look as good as you feel</li>\r\n	<li>Professional  link back to military qualities (integrity, reliability, timeliness, ability to handle stressful situations)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width="1/1"][uxb_divider style="special"][uxb_heading text="Questions You May Have" type="h3" has_line="false" icon_size="16"][vc_accordion use_as="accordion" collapsible="yes" active_section="1" expanded="true"][vc_accordion_tab title="Normal Text"][vc_column_text]Mauris mauris ante, blandit et, ultrices a, suscipit eget, quam. Integer ut neque. Vivamus nisi metus, molestie vel, gravida in, condimentum sit amet, nunc. Nam a nibh. Donec suscipit eros. Nam mi. Proin viverra leo ut odio. Curabitur malesuada. Vestibulum a velit eu ante scelerisque vulputate.[/vc_column_text][/vc_accordion_tab][vc_accordion_tab title="Text with List Item"][vc_column_text]Nam enim risus, molestie et, porta ac, aliquam ac, risus. Quisque lobortis. Phasellus pellentesque purus in massa. Aenean in pede. Phasellus ac libero ac tellus pellentesque semper. Sed ac felis. Sed commodo, magna quis lacinia ornare, quam ante aliquam nisi, eu iaculis leo purus venenatis dui