(331, 1, '2015-03-05 06:38:01', '2015-03-05 06:38:01', '[vc_row][vc_column width="1/1"][vc_column_text]Melissa and James were married four years ago and disaster struck when their wedding photographer did not show up to their wedding! Karen Alsop from Emerald Eye Photography in Victoria decided to help utilise a wedding photography retreat to allow James and Melissa to finally get the wedding photos they deserved. I was privileged to be attending the wedding retreat and here is a small selection of the photos I captured for this special couple. Melissa and James also utilised the opportunity to renew their vows. I hope these images form their wedding album for them to hand down to their children.[/vc_column_text][uxb_divider style="special"][vc_gallery images="333,334,335,336,337,338,339,340" type="image_grid" grid_style="square" img_size="full" columns="col4" onclick="link_image" interval="5" show_bullets="true"][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'Their Wedding Photographer Didn''t Turn Up To The Wedding!', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'their-wedding-photographer-didnt-turn-up-to-the-wedding', '', '', '2015-03-05 06:46:02', '2015-03-05 06:46:02', '', 0, 'http://localhost/samantha-ohlsen-photography/?p=331', 12, 'post', '', 0),
